translation[12]{c,v,t}:
  35,19,Abafani abaziimfama nababonayo
  35,20,Bungafani kananjalo ubumnyama nobumhlophe
  35,21,Nomthunzi nobushushu
  35,22,"Abafani abaphilayo nabafileyo. Inene, uAllâh Wenza kuve lowo Athande (ukuba eve), kodwa awungekhe ubenze bave abo basemangcwabeni"
  35,23,"Wena (Muhammad), awunto (yimbi) ngaphandle kokuba nguMlumkisi"
  35,24,Inene wena Sikuthumele ngenyaniso ukuba ube nguMvakalisi weendaba ezilungileyo noMlumkisi. Kananjalo akukho luhlanga lungazanga lube naMphaphamisi uphila phakathi kwalo
  35,25,Ke kaloku ukuba baya kuphika wena sele babaphika kakade nabangaphambili kunabo. AbaThunywa babo beza kubo benemiqondiso ecacileyo nemigaqo ebhaliweyo neziBhalo ezilukhanyiselo
  35,26,"Ndaza Ndabahlasela abangakholwayo, saba njani ke isohlwayo saM"
  35,27,"Akuboni na ukuba uAllâh Uthumela imvula ivela esibhakabhakeni, Size Sivelise iziqhamo ngayo zemibala yonke eyahlukeneyo? (eminye yayo) imnyama kakhulu"
  35,28,"Ke kaloku phakathi kwabantu nezidalwa ezinyakazayo nemfuyo edla ingca zinemibala eziintlobo ngeentlobo ngokufanayo. Kuphela kwizicaka zaKhe ngabo bamoyikayo uAllâh abanolwazi. Inene uAllâh Unobunganga, nguMxoleli"
  35,29,"Inene abo bacengceleza iNcwadi ka-Allâh, bamisela iSalâh banikele kumalizo ngoko Sibaphe kona, emfihlakalweni okanye ekuhleni mabalindele umvuzo ongasokuze uphele"
  35,30,"Kwanokuba Uza kubanika umvuzo wabo ngokugcweleyo Abongezelele ububele baKhe. Inene, uAllâh nguMxoleli, Obulelayo"